---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';

const title = 'Privacy Policy';
const description = 'Privacy Policy for Christian Tech Help';
const pubDate = new Date('February 06 2026');
---
<Layout title={title} description={description} pubDate={pubDate}>

  <p>Last updated: February 06, 2026</p>

  <p>We only collect information we need to help you. We do not sell your information. We use it to provide tech support, schedule visits, send updates or invoices, and communicate with you about your request.</p>

  <h2>Information we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Name</li>
    <li>Phone number</li>
    <li>Email address</li>
    <li>Address (if on-site service is needed)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Payments</h2>
  <p>If you pay online, payments are processed by Square (Block, Inc.). We do not store your full payment card details. You can read Square’s Privacy Notice at <a href="https://squareup.com/us/en/legal/general/privacy">https://squareup.com/us/en/legal/general/privacy</a>.</p>

  <h2>Emails and newsletters</h2>
  <p>If you choose to subscribe, we use MailerLite to send emails. You can unsubscribe at any time using the link in the email. MailerLite’s Privacy Policy is at <a href="https://www.mailerlite.com/legal/privacy-policy">https://www.mailerlite.com/legal/privacy-policy</a>.</p>

  <h2>Website analytics and cookies</h2>
  <p>We use Google Analytics to understand basic website traffic (such as page views and time on site). You can disable cookies in your browser if you prefer. Google’s Privacy Policy is at <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy">https://policies.google.com/privacy</a> and the opt-out tool is at <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout">https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout</a>.</p>

  <h2>How we share information</h2>
  <p>We only share information with the service providers above (Square, MailerLite, and Google Analytics) or if required by law.</p>

  <h2>How long we keep information</h2>
  <p>We keep information only as long as needed to provide service and maintain basic records, then delete it.</p>

  <h2>Children’s privacy</h2>
  <p>We do not knowingly collect personal information from anyone under 16.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>If you have questions, email <a href="mailto:scott@christiantechhelp.com">scott@christiantechhelp.com</a>.</p>
</Layout>
